{"tid":123914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俠之大者 圍毆一人","createTime":"2017-02-17T07:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T07:52:18.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3847b7c018d747c28693bc9835b64dc36aea226a","tid":123914,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"七警案今日判刑，案中7名警員被判囚兩年。身為律師會前會長的獨立建制派議員何君堯在facebook貼文，為他們發聲，以「The Magnificent Seven」為題，指「七警被判入獄兩年，確重！上訴減刑是可料的！今天七警被變成七俠了！」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯之前與傳媒茶敘時，已認為7人「情有可原」，因他們不是貪贓枉法，只是想對示威者小懲大誡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲真恐怖，用私刑成大俠<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得港女會歌頌isis"},{"pid":"0d4b119f45e71dc3952bca4d5bee9040f42d4d65","tid":123914,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:46:30.000Z","msg":"The Magnificent Seven 有三個死咗㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7511db5b805b6e913a0ad5361490727e8efb17bd","tid":123914,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"何生唔係喺法庭自拍，被人攪緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26fbaf3efd8c9d573fd697369fbe32083b47fb5","tid":123914,"uid":38615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:52:18.000Z","msg":"俠之大者，圍毆一人<br />\n知法犯法，情有可原"}]}